arStrings.szText: "Telan attacked me. He had been seeing visions, hearing voices. He was offered the power of a Hellborne, and he accepted."
That damned boy. This is what the demons intended. To fill us with undeserved strength...and die on the blade of our comrades. That damned, damned boy.
furious, but wracked with guilt, despairing
And what's worse? I've begun to hear them tooâ€”the sweet whispers in the dark. They promise the world. And they would take me, as they took Telan. As they took Shon and Ysad.
softly, an admission, with a bitter laugh.
I will never give in. No hellspawn will turn me against my own. But I need time to think. Continue your work. We will speak again soon.
summoning her resolve, bitterness in her gut, a plan forming in her mind
